    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p>Frost-draugr are the heavy infantry of the undead host — bloated, rimed corpses that radiate numbing cold in an aura around their bodies. They were buried warriors encased in permafrost, and the cold has become part of their undead flesh. Clustered together in marching platoons, their chill aura can freeze the ground underfoot and bite through armor. They are slow but nearly impossible to stop.</p>",
        "public": ""
